    <div class="tag">Compiled by Gemini 2.5 Pro</div>
    <h1>Vertex Pharmaceuticals (VRTX)<br/>Intrinsic Value</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A transparent, two-stage discounted cash flow valuation of Vertex Pharmaceuticals — using FY2025 actuals, disclosed assumptions, and one final number.</p>
    <p class="date">Updated March 18, 2026 · Data: FY2025 10-K</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <!-- ═══ THE VERDICT ═══ -->
